cs.IT, cs.COMM, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MA. 

This paper deals with moment generating functions of generalized fading models in wireless communication theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves analytical manipulations and evaluation of bit error rates, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.MA (Machine Learning).
